patches./Deployment-jaeger-collector.yaml:
apiVersion: extensions/v1beta1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: jaeger
    jaeger-infra: collector-deployment
  name: jaeger-collector
spec:
  template:
    spec:
      $setElementOrder/containers:
      - name: jaeger-collector
      containers:
      - $setElementOrder/ports:
        - containerPort: 14267
        - containerPort: 14268
        - containerPort: 9411
        name: jaeger-collector
        ports:
        - containerPort: 14268
          protocol: TCP
        - $patch: delete
          containerPort: FORKED_PORT
patches./Deployment-jaeger-query.yaml:
apiVersion: extensions/v1beta1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  labels:
    app: jaeger
    jaeger-infra: query-deployment
  name: jaeger-query
spec:
  template:
    spec:
      $setElementOrder/containers:
      - name: jaeger-query
      containers:
      - $setElementOrder/env:
        - name: SPAN_STORAGE_TYPE
        env:
        - name: SPAN_STORAGE_TYPE
          valueFrom:
            configMapKeyRef:
              key: span-storage-type
              name: jaeger-configuration
        - $patch: delete
          name: FORKED_ENV
        name: jaeger-query
